Name: Hentai Series: Classic
About the game: Hentai Series is the game where you have to complete 8 puzzles by moving blocks and collect images of girls after completing level. It's a great moment when your imagination becomes reality and no one can stop you... A - Auto complete level. F - Game self-destruction mode (close the game in one moment).| Arrows - Navigate through gallery and levels. Meet unknown women, will you know their name's... stories? All you can see now is their appearence. Should you play a detective game to understand who they are?
